*****************************************************************************************************
JB Bioinformatics Pipeline Project V3
Creation of piepline with end-to-end functionality. Able to fully process a sample without error. 

Tool Order:    
        Dataset Input - gather raw data to process in pipeline
        Fastq - gather quality metrics from fastq files
        MultiQC - collat indiviual quality metric into one file 
        MarkDuplicates - examine aligned in BAM datasets to locate and remove duplicates
        Re-align Reads - Correcting the misalignments around insertions and deletions, an alternative to BamLeftAlign
        Insert indel qualities - Adding the indel qualities into our alignment file via Insert indel qualities
        Call variants - call varinats with lowfreq
        SnpEff eff - Annotate variants called 
        SnpEff eff Extract Fields - Extrcat clinally relevant varinats called 
        Collapse Collection - presents annotated variants into a single dataset 
        
Comments:
        Removal of tools:Trimmomatic, BWA-MEM2, Falco, BamLeftAlign and GEMINI

*****************************************************************************************************
